attachments.title: Raspberry Pi Zero: the $5 computer - Raspberry Pi
attachments.text: Of all the things we do at Raspberry Pi, driving down the cost of computer hardware remains one of the most important. Even in the developed world, a programmable computer is a luxury item for a lot of people, and every extra dollar that we ask someone to spend decreases the chance that they’ll choose …
